{"tid":2137701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廢糧曝光 中儲糧禁攜手機","createTime":"2020-08-03T06:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T10:18:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b23bf6ec9ce5ca47d45a21776a1530f2cc865bb1","tid":2137701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200803/WWG7U7CO6ZT4POFTTZ7WOEGYXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200803%2FWWG7U7CO6ZT4POFTTZ7WOEGYXI%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=1cd00153\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200803%2FWWG7U7CO6ZT4POFTTZ7WOEGYXI%2F&h=fef94adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200803/WWG7U7CO6ZT4POFTTZ7WOEGYXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n廢糧曝光 中儲糧禁攜手機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FQb2UVCwtYsNpKJ0otR0mou9HEQ=/190x285/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/62XQ6CZAAQMQQSPRIHNY4NRFJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFQb2UVCwtYsNpKJ0otR0mou9HEQ%3D%2F190x285%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F62XQ6CZAAQMQQSPRIHNY4NRFJA.jpg&h=dfede91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中儲糧的粟米被揭滲入雜質。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n「改變不了我，就改變你！」中國網民調侃近日中儲糧黑龍江分公司發出的一個新通告，要求外來人員不得帶同手機和錄像錄音設備進入倉庫。早前中儲糧黑龍江分公司肇東直屬庫一個儲庫，被揭發儲備的粟米質素差劣，惹來關注；網民質問新通知的用意：「你在怕甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民質疑「在怕甚麼」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。進入庫區的客戶必須將手機存放到保安指定的儲存櫃。通告下款是中央儲備糧肇州直屬庫有限公司，發出日期為2020年7月28日。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。6月19日她在拍賣中購下5,000噸一次性儲備糧，惟儲糧品質差劣，她在片中示範一手把粟米碎成兩半，指縫間還有變成粉狀的碎渣。王麗更稱，粟米堆中摻入了「篩下物」，存在大量雜質，粟米還有酸味。<br />\n<br />\n中儲糧上月中指經初步核查，影片反映的粟米質素問題與事實基本不符，只屬個別粟米問題，不代表整倉的質素。<br />\n<br />\n網易"},{"pid":"9a112390ab5ac05a5c4b6c9bcdc0550f7f68ea49","tid":2137701,"uid":77968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"磨碎做粟粉再整粟米片<br />\n加啲糖同味粉就食唔出"},{"pid":"ec22583583ee8d1dd8020960b857fd59ff5a27b0","tid":2137701,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee070557473300d7d648ee4266162c7011a0206a","tid":2137701,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"刁帝幾時會降旨浮筷落人頭"},{"pid":"697ca7235a29fcfb30df9e22336eab126d81d056","tid":2137701,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"溝沙飽肚啲架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7359faac484f375dbc370f9f6d034824606168b9","tid":2137701,"uid":356218,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1966fecf8db19e81f815ffbe14bb814778e8a760","tid":2137701,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"化驗成份，含豐富礦物質"},{"pid":"9af9f6a341815d79fab1b3315dc3ef9f239dcd82","tid":2137701,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1966fecf8db19e81f815ffbe14bb814778e8a760","tid":2137701,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"化驗成份，含豐富礦物質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de7c1ccf587c08350f25ce0e8d3ad01c418e463","tid":2137701,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"6月19日她在拍賣中購下5,000噸一次性儲備糧<br />\n<br />\n邊到有唔係一次性既糧食賣?"},{"pid":"0150ac82d76c15d6de1fb97b5c59e8a539970a80","tid":2137701,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit